   +------------------------+------------------------------------------+
   | DELEGATED              | Valid acceptance signature received,     |
   |                        | responsibility transferred to Delegatee. |
   +------------------------+------------------------------------------+
   | TERMINATED_ARCHIVED    | Terminated state, all three tiers retained |
   |                        | for long-term compliance audit.            |
   +------------------------+------------------------------------------+
   | TERMINATED_ERASED      | Terminated state, Tier 3 logic payload     |
   |                        | cryptographically erased (satisfying     |
   |                        | right to be forgotten).                  |
   +------------------------+------------------------------------------+
   | DISPUTED_FROZEN        | Dispute detected, chain frozen pending     |
