   | Attack Type    | Description                    | Mitigation    |
   +----------------+--------------------------------+---------------+
   | Signature      | Attacker forges Ed25519         | Key in        |
   | Forgery        | signature                      | HSM/TEE       |
   +----------------+--------------------------------+---------------+
   | Hash Collision | Find different judgments with   | Use SHA-256   |
   |                | same hash                       |               |
