G.5.3.  GDPR Compliance Proof

   Extension Identifier: org.ietf.jep.ext.gdpr-proof
   Compatibility: full
   Priority: Priority 4 (Compliance Support)

   Purpose: Provide cryptographic proof of GDPR compliance for
