       "dpo_signature": "base64-dpo-sig",
       "audit_log": ["audit-event-1", "audit-event-2"]
     }
   }
   ```

   Verification Rules:
   - If termination_mode is "ERASED", gdpr.erasure_proof MUST be
     present
   - erasure_timestamp MUST be within ±5 seconds of $Terminate
     event timestamp
   - If DPO signature configured, verify signature validity
   - Audit logs SHOULD support EDPB required "case-by-case
